        "content": "## PostgreSQL Backup Configuration\n\n- **Schedule**: Daily at 2 AM UTC\n  - Cron: `0 2 * * *`\n- **Databases**: \n  - nvisnx\n  - nxmain\n  - alerts_db\n- **Retention**: 30 days\n- **Destination**: S3 bucket\n  - `nvisionx-postgres-backup-3848ba22`\n- **Compression**: Enabled\n- **Parallel Jobs**: 2\n\n---\n\n⚠️ **Note**: Investigate failed backups immediately. Check pod logs for details.",
